<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Genderbase</h1>

  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-4xl">
    <p class="mb-4">Genderbase is a community-driven platform dedicated to providing accurate, supportive information about gender identity, expression, and diversity. Our mission is to create a safe space where people can learn, share experiences, and find answers to their questions about gender.</p>

    <p class="mb-4">Founded in 2023 by a diverse group of individuals with personal and professional experience in gender issues, Genderbase aims to bridge the knowledge gap that often exists around gender topics and provide resources that are accessible to everyone.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Respect:</strong> We honor all gender identities and expressions without judgment.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We are committed to providing factual, up-to-date information.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We strive to make our platform accessible and welcoming to people from all backgrounds.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Community:</strong> We believe in the power of shared knowledge and experiences.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Privacy:</strong> We respect user privacy and maintain confidentiality.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">Genderbase provides a range of resources, including:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">A Q&A platform where users can ask questions about gender and receive thoughtful, informed responses</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A knowledge base with articles and resources on gender-related topics</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A comprehensive terminology guide</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Community-contributed articles sharing personal insights and experiences</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-4">We believe that understanding gender diversity is essential for creating a more inclusive and accepting society. By providing accurate information and fostering meaningful dialogue, we hope to contribute to this important goal.</p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <a href="/team" class="btn btn-primary mr-4">Meet Our Team</a>
      <a href="/volunteer" class="btn btn-outline">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
